### --- Prerequisites: Create a drone first ---

### Create Drone (for mission tests)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SKY-MS01-TE5T",
  "model": "PHANTOM_4"
}

### --- Mission CRUD ---

### Create Mission
POST http://localhost:3000/api/missions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wind Farm Alpha Inspection",
  "type": "WIND_TURBINE_INSPECTION",
  "droneId": "{{droneId}}",
  "pilotName": "John Doe",
  "siteLocation": "Wind Farm Alpha - North Sector",
  "plannedStartTime": "2027-01-15T10:00:00Z",
  "plannedEndTime": "2027-01-15T14:00:00Z"
}

### List Missions (paginated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/missions?page=1&limit=10

### List Missions (filtered by status)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/missions?status=PLANNED

### List Missions (filtered by droneId)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/missions?droneId={{droneId}}

### Get Mission by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/missions/{{missionId}}

### --- State Transitions ---

### Transition: PLANNED → PRE_FLIGHT_CHECK
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/missions/{{missionId}}/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PRE_FLIGHT_CHECK"
}

### Transition: PRE_FLIGHT_CHECK → IN_PROGRESS
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/missions/{{missionId}}/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Transition: IN_PROGRESS → COMPLETED
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/missions/{{missionId}}/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "flightHours": 2.5
}

### Transition: PLANNED → ABORTED (with reason)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/missions/{{missionId}}/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ABORTED",
  "abortReason": "Weather conditions deteriorated"
}

### Transition: PLANNED → ABORTED (without reason — should fail 422)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/missions/{{missionId}}/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ABORTED"
}

### Transition: PLANNED → ABORTED (with reason)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/missions/{{missionId}}/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ABORTED",
  "abortReason": "Client requested cancellation"
}

### --- Validation Error Cases ---

### Invalid: Schedule in the past (should fail 422)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/missions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Past Mission",
  "type": "SOLAR_PANEL_SURVEY",
  "droneId": "{{droneId}}",
  "pilotName": "Jane",
  "siteLocation": "Solar Farm",
  "plannedStartTime": "2020-01-01T10:00:00Z",
  "plannedEndTime": "2020-01-01T14:00:00Z"
}

### Invalid: End before start (should fail 422)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/missions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bad Times",
  "type": "POWER_LINE_PATROL",
  "droneId": "{{droneId}}",
  "pilotName": "Jane",
  "siteLocation": "Power Line Grid",
  "plannedStartTime": "2027-06-01T14:00:00Z",
  "plannedEndTime": "2027-06-01T10:00:00Z"
}

### Invalid: Overlapping mission (should fail 409 — run Create Mission first)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/missions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Overlapping Mission",
  "type": "SOLAR_PANEL_SURVEY",
  "droneId": "{{droneId}}",
  "pilotName": "Jane",
  "siteLocation": "Solar Farm",
  "plannedStartTime": "2027-01-15T12:00:00Z",
  "plannedEndTime": "2027-01-15T16:00:00Z"
}

### Invalid: Invalid transition (should fail 422)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/missions/{{missionId}}/transition
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### Invalid: Missing droneId (should fail 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/missions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No Drone",
  "type": "WIND_TURBINE_INSPECTION",
  "pilotName": "Jane",
  "siteLocation": "Site",
  "plannedStartTime": "2027-06-01T10:00:00Z",
  "plannedEndTime": "2027-06-01T14:00:00Z"
}
